    • Method Detail

      • prettyPrint

        String prettyPrint(String message)
        Transforms the message into a pretty-printed format. Implementations should:
        1. Sanitize the message by replacing any sensitive information with a token such as REDACTED.
        2. Return the original message if an exception occurs during formatting.
        Parameters:
        message - the message to be pretty printed
        Returns:
        the given message in pretty-printed format
